ALLOW_DEV_OTP=1




 Homework-Whisper — Realtime Chat (OTP auth + images)

A minimal, production-style chat app built with Vite + React + Socket.IO + Express + Prisma (SQLite).
Login via email OTP (dev-friendly), send text or images (drag & drop / paste), see realtime updates, and delete your own messages.

 Features

🔐 OTP login → JWT (dev mode supported)

🔄 Realtime messages via Socket.IO

💬 Text messages + 🖼️ image upload (drag & drop, paste)

✅ Auth-protected REST API (/api/*)

🧹 Delete your own messages

🚦 Simple anti-spam rate limit (e.g. 8 messages / 5s per user)

🗂️ SQLite persistence via Prisma; images stored in /uploads

🧰 Dev-friendly email options: Dev OTP return / Ethereal Preview / Brevo (real)

willing to add pagination 


Frontend: React 18, Vite, react-dropzone, Socket.IO client

Backend: Express, Socket.IO, Multer (uploads), Prisma (SQLite), Zod, JWT

Email: Brevo (prod) or Nodemailer Ethereal (dev demo)


